<section class="hero">

<h1>
Environmental <span>Science</span>
</h1>

<p>
Environmental microbiomics studies microbial communities across soil, water, air, built environments, and ecosystems, revealing how microbes shape environmental health, nutrient cycling, contamination, climate systems, and ecological resilience.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
